Description: Keyboard-driven terminal BattleTech record-sheet tracker (Classic, Alpha
 Strike, and more).
 Neurohelmet is a keyboard-driven terminal (TUI) tracker for BattleTech record
 sheets, covering Classic BattleTech, Alpha Strike, and several other game
 modes. The full unit dataset is embedded in the binary, so it runs fully
 offline with no external files.

